      "settings": {
        "title": "",
        "subtitle": "2. Pairs Seamlessly With Your iPhone",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/adventorial-3.webp",
        "content": "<p>Leaving your Apple Watch at home doesn’t mean going dark.<br/><br/>You still need to know when the boss is calling, when dispatch needs something, or when your family is trying to reach you. The last thing you want is to be elbow-deep in a job and digging around for your phone every five minutes.<br/><br/>With a rugged work watch like <a href=\"/products/carbinox-blaze\" title=\"Carbinox Blaze Smartwatch – Ultimate Pack\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>the Carbinox Blaze</strong></span></a><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>,</strong></span> you still see who’s calling. You still read texts. You still get notifications right on your wrist while your phone stays in your pocket, on the bench, or in the truck.<br/><br/>No fumbling with a slippery phone around tools. No pulling it out near edges, pits, ladders, or heavy equipment. You stay connected where it matters, without needing your Apple Watch on the front lines.<br/><br/></p>",
