        "image": "shopify://shop_images/11_1_2.webp",
        "content": "<p>If it’s going to be your work watch, it has to prove it.<br/><br/>That’s why <a href=\"/products/carbinox-blaze\" title=\"Carbinox Blaze Smartwatch – Ultimate Pack\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Carbinox doesn’t ask you to just “trust” it.</strong></span></a> You get a <strong>45-day risk-free trial</strong> to see if this watch actually earns its place on your wrist. You wear it to work. You bang it. You scratch it. You sweat in it. You see if it makes your day easier, not harder.<br/><br/>If it doesn’t feel right, doesn’t fit your routine, or just doesn’t impress you, you can send it back within that window. No guessing. No getting stuck with something you don’t use.<br/><br/>On top of that, it’s backed by a <strong>Lifetime Replacement Warranty.</strong> If it ever fails or breaks under normal use, it’s covered. That’s not something you hear often in the smartwatch world—especially not for something built to live in grease, dust, and concrete.<br/><br/>Instead of gambling the life of your Apple Watch every shift, you get a <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>work watch that’s built for abuse and backed for life.</strong></span></p>",
